# DevOps E-commerce Website

This is a simple e-commerce website project that demonstrates the use of HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and a basic backend setup with Node.js and Express. The project also showcases basic DevOps practices including project structure organization and static file serving.

## Project Structure

```plaintext
project-root/
├── server.js           # Node.js server setup
├── package.json        # Project dependencies and scripts
├── views/              # Folder containing HTML files
│   ├── home.html
│   ├── about.html
│   ├── contact.html
│   └── ...
├── images/             # Folder containing image files
│   ├── logo.png
│   ├── background.jpg
│   └── ...
└── db/                 # Folder containing database connection file
    └── connection.js
